The paper deals with the performance analysis of mixed-ADC massive MIMO systems, which involves signal processing, communication, and networking aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the fundamental limits of data communication and storage. The second likely category is cs.COMM (Networking and Internet Architecture), which deals with the design and analysis of communication systems and networks. The third likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), which deals with the modeling, analysis, and control of complex systems. The fourth likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which deals with the processing, analysis, and retrieval of multimedia data. The fifth likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), which deals with the design, implementation, and evaluation of computer networks and protocols.
